data.description: Welcome Home to this 3 Bedroom 1 Bath ranch style home. Upon entry, you're welcomed into a spacious living room. Outside, enjoy the serene backyard with plenty of room for gardening, relaxation, and outdoor activities. There is a roomy 2 car detached garage with a covered breezeway. The basement is plumbed for a full bathroom which is partially completed. Transferable waterproofing was completed in October 2022.
